item.title: Hello World From a Human Person
item.description: I’m Eileen Noonan. I’m an actress. I’m a writer. I’m a computer programmer. I try to be a good friend, a good sister, a good daughter, a good aunt, a good person. I don’t know that I’ll ever get to be a mother of any kind. I’m transgender. First and foremost I am a human fucking being. Can we all be human beings? I suppose that’s a question that’s been plaguing me lately.
